des: Discover a fresh take on music with MNPR Radio, your go-to source for alternative sounds. Brought to you by MNPR Magazine, MNPR Radio is a curated selection of indie, rock, blues, and underground music that breaks away from the ordinary. Whether you're looking to explore new artists or dive into exclusive tracks, MNPR Radio keeps you connected to the pulse of alternative music. Just ask Alexa to play MNPR Radio and experience the sound of the underground.
